# GlanceSearch .gitignore

## Internal / planning docs (not for public repo)
GlanceSearch App PRD.md
build_output.txt
build_log.txt

## .NET build output
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/[Bb]in/
**/[Oo]bj/
out/
publish/
build/

## IDE / User-specific
.vs/
.vscode/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.rsuser
*.DotSettings.user
launchSettings.json

## NuGet
packages/
*.nupkg
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json

## JetBrains Rider
.idea/
*.sln.iml
*.ipr
*.iws

## OS files
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store
._*
[Dd]esktop.ini

## Debug / logs
*.log
logs/

## Test results
TestResults/
coverage/
*.trx

## Self-contained publish output (built artifacts, not source)
*.exe

## Installer source scripts are tracked; built artifacts are not
## NSIS output
installer/Output/
installer/*.exe

## Runtime / temp
artifacts/
BenchmarkDotNet.Artifacts/

## Database files (user data — never commit)
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

## Tesseract trained data (downloaded at runtime, not part of source)
tessdata/*.traineddata
tessdata/

## User settings and captures (generated at runtime)
## (These live in %AppData%\GlanceSearch, not in the project, but listed for safety)
captures/
captures-thumb/

## Secrets / environment
.env
.env.*
secrets.json
appsettings.Development.json

## Archives
*.zip
*.7z
*.rar
*.tar.gz
